data.description: This 2BR/2BA home is situated on a corner lot in the centrally located Lakeside development. The home comes "unfurnished", so bring your own style and make this your cute & cozy residence. The home is tiled throughout, and comes complete w/a breakfast bar, 2 tile baths, granite countertops, AND a 2-stall garage!! Just a short walk to the community clubhouse & pool at the entrance to Lakeside or the unique lap pool at the east end of the community. Lakeside has many amenities that include Pickleball, Tennis Courts (Har-Tru), Shuffleboard, 2-story Clubhouse, Community Pool, Lap Pool, Exercise Room, Fishing Pier, 1-1/2 Mile sidewalk inside the perimeter, a 40-acre lake to kayak or enjoy a quiet ride in your non-motorized boat. Close to Collier County Government Center, Collier County Library, Collier County Schools, Restaurants, Shopping, Marinas and so much more!
